{"tid":623555,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求助被拒　泰裔婦燒鄧家彪議辦候懲","createTime":"2018-04-10T05:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T10:26:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7311ab5ae8b36fb018c7cbf4f38dcfce58f41682","tid":623555,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180410/20356949?_ga=2.111944708.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F20356949%3F_ga%3D2.111944708.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=aPFo5rXQnvv5auJGqgD5WOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=f0083a9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F20356949%3F_ga%3D2.111944708.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=d41c4d99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180410/20356949?_ga=2.111944708.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n求助被拒　泰裔婦燒鄧家彪議辦候懲<br />\n<br />\n3.1K<br />\n法庭<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180410/large/10ls3p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180410%2Flarge%2F10ls3p1.jpg&h=7239d6ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n案中鄧家彪議員辦事處的大門被焚毀。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日兼兩職辛勤養家的泰裔港婦稱不甘遭陌生男無端當街指罵是「雞」，向當區區議員鄧家彪求助不果，再向社區服務中心要求跟進又遭拒，一怒之下先後在議員辦事處及中心縱火洩憤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n律師誤稱鄧剛當選立會<br />\n<br />\n泰裔婦昨承認兩項縱火罪，辯方呈上鄧家彪的求情信，卻誤稱他剛當選立法會議員。被告還柙至本月23日宣判，等候精神科醫生及背景報告。<br />\n<br />\n案發於去年10月2日國慶日補假下午，41歲被告Sunisa Wan先在東涌逸東邨鄧家彪議員辦事處門外放火，燒毀大門及膠簾，其後到邨內鄰舍輔導會綜合服務中心放火，惟火勢很快自行熄滅。<br />\n<br />\n被告有高空擲物及藏有武器案底。辯方求情指她生於泰國，早年移居本港並嫁給港人，現育有16歲女兒，居於東涌公屋。被告丈夫本為保安，3年前中風，被告獨力養家，在機場當清潔工和餐館任廚師，從無怨言。被告雖有飲酒習慣，但還柙期間已戒掉。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指本案緣於被告去年6月在區內遭陌生男子指罵是「雞」。她向鄧求助，望找出該男子，但鄧稱「非常難做，做唔到」；她復向鄰舍輔導會求助，希望社工跟進，但對方坦言安排不到。辯方指丈夫願代賠償鄧申索的3,500元維修費。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC1062/17<br />\n■記者楊家樂"},{"pid":"c63b7b18eda02431d3eadb138ff67bbbc98d9941","tid":623555,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:29:43.000Z","msg":"俾人鬧都可以搵議員？"},{"pid":"769c72b2a8756d37c6de3bcc95a6c37391e10f41","tid":623555,"uid":62494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:31:35.000Z","msg":"辯方呈上鄧家彪的求情信，卻誤稱他剛當選立法會議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf9801ced2abbe6cfc5fdeab5ce80291cbc21a3","tid":623555,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"俾人告燒鄧家彪議員辦事處，可唔可以搵鄧家彪議員求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78334b548159390accf6587e7d1da31e1e874e5","tid":623555,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:10:50.000Z","msg":"41歲，要叫都叫老雞"},{"pid":"70c52ddb72ed545b885da2b33fd79b9799d26e25","tid":623555,"uid":5419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T09:53:26.000Z","msg":"真。勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 秦國人好波"},{"pid":"4de1cb82504b36730cfd62d541a4dd3b58559e7d","tid":623555,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"條鄧家彪明玩野<br />\n<br />\n以前我試過跨區叫立法會議員幫都有人幫<br />\n因為我樓下條區佬選完消失左"},{"pid":"0dea5235b7f1eab425fd27b7e53094feca9205bc","tid":623555,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a7cb8bf84e58bfbddde0391e441e4d8e6948f26","tid":623555,"uid":15358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"泰式焦土派"},{"pid":"70bfe0dcc87b44cc71fbf090f97fed455a423889","tid":623555,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\